election_record.label: Vermont 1821 Council

overview.note: The Original Election Returns Aggregates tally sheet lists 12216 votes for Joseph Berry, 12138 votes for Seth Wetmore, 11549 votes for Timothy Stanley, 9914 votes for Charles Phelps, 10115 votes for Josiah Dana, 9708 votes for Truman Chittenden, 9510 votes for Henry Olin, 9067 votes for Ezra Butler, 7609 votes for John H. Andrus, 7107 votes for Aaron Leland, 7055 votes for William Strong and 2558 votes for Eben H. Judd.

The Original Election Returns Aggregates tally sheet lists some county totals for Ezra Meach, William Nutting and Jonas Clark, but they are not added uThe sums for these entries are 1332 votes for Ezra Meach, 585 votes for William Nutting and 183 votes for Jonas Clark.

The Vermont Republican and American Yeoman (Windsor, VT), The Vermont Journal (Windsor, VT) and Woodstock Observer (Woodstock, VT) report 12216 votes for Joseph Berry, 12138 votes for Seth Wetmore, 11549 votes for Timothy Stanley, 9914 votes for Charles Phelps, 10115 votes for Josiah Dana, 9708 votes for Truman Chittenden, 9010 votes for Henry Olin, 9067 votes for Ezra Butler, 7609 votes for John H. Andrus, 7107 votes for Aaron Leland, 7055 votes for William Strong, 3553 votes for Samuel Prentiss, 2558 votes for Eben H. Judd, 1333 votes for Ezra Meach, 585 votes for William Nutting and 183 votes for Jonas Clark.

The Vermont Intelligencer, and Bellows Falls Advertiser (Bellows Falls, VT) reports 12246 votes for Joseph Berry, 12138 votes for Seth Wetmore, 11549 votes for Timothy Stanley, 9914 votes for Charles Phelps, 10115 votes for Josiah Dana, 9708 votes for Truman Chittenden, 9010 votes for Henry Olin, 9067 votes for Ezra Butler, 7609 votes for John H. Andrus, 7107 votes for Aaron Leland, 7055 votes for William Strong, 3553 votes for Samuel Prentiss, 2558 votes for Eben H. Judd, 1333 votes for Ezra Meach, 585 votes for William Nutting and 183 votes for Jonas Clark.

The Watchman (Montpelier, VT) reports 12216 votes for Joseph Berry, 12138 votes for Seth Wetmore, 11549 votes for Timothy Stanley, 9914 votes for Charles Phelps, 10115 votes for Josiah Dana, 9708 votes for Truman Chittenden, 9510 votes for Henry Olin, 9067 votes for Ezra Butler, 7609 votes for John H. Andrus, 7107 votes for Aaron Leland, 7058 votes for William Strong, 3555 votes for Samuel Prentiss and 2558 votes for Eben H. Judd.
